        <!-- Notable Things I Did -->
        <section class="project-section">
            <h2>Highlight of the Project</h2>
            <p>Reflecting on the project, the aspect that fills me with the most pride are the character controls. One of the 
                focuses and ideas behind this project was simplifying things down, focuses in on content and feel. The
                three hit sword animation has a satisfying timing to it. I find that moving around has the simple fun to it that
                I was looking for in ways that some previous projects lacked. That said it this game is also a bit even-keeled,
                one thing I wanted expand upon in the future is those moments of excitement.</p>
        </section>

